.SH "NAME"
update_ini \- converts 2\&.7 format INI files to 2\&.8 format
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBupdate_ini\fR [\fB\-f\fR] [\fB\-d\fR] \fI<INI\fR file>_
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBupdate_ini\fR is run automatically by the "linuxcnc" script when an INI file in the pre\-joints\-axes format is opened\&.
.sp
\-d causes a dialog box to be shown asking if the script should be run\&.
.sp
\-f is designed for auto\-conversion and will not create the backup files\&.
